quran[15{c,v,t}:
23,60,aur jo day satke hain dete hain aur un ke dil is baat se drtay rehtay hain ke un ko apne perwar-digaar ki lout kar jana hai
23,61,yahi log nakiyon mein jaldi kere aur yahi unn ke liye agay nikal jatay hain
23,62,aur hum kisi shakhs ko is ki taaqat se ziyada takleef nahi dete aur hamaray paas kitaab hai jo sach sach keh deti hai aur un logon par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
23,63,"magar un ke dil un ( baton ) ki taraf se ghaflat mein ( parre hue ) hain, aur un ke siwa aur aamaal bhi hain jo yeh karte rehtay hain"
23,64,yahan taq ke jab hum ne un mein se aasooda haal logon ko pakar liya to woh is waqt chalayein ge
23,65,aaj mat chalao! tum ko hum se kuch madad nahi miley gi
23,66,meri ayatain tum ko parh parh kar sunai jati theen aur tum ultay paon phir phir jatay they
23,67,"un se sar kashi karte, kahaaniyon mein mashgool hotay aur behooda bakwaas karte they"
23,68,kiya unhon ne is kalaam mein ghhor nahikiya ya un ke paas koi aisi cheez aayi hai jo un ke aglay baap dada ke paas nahi thi
23,69,"ya yeh apne paighambar ko jantay pehjantay nahi, is wajah se un ko nahi mantay"
23,70,kiya yeh kehte hain ke usay soda hai ( nahi ) balkay woh un ke paas haq ko le kar aeye hain aur un mein se aksar haq ko napasand karte hain
23,71,aur khuday-e ( barhaq ) un ki khawahishon par chalay to aasman aur zameen aur jo un mein hain sab darham barham ho jaien. balkay hum ne un ke paas un ki nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) pouncha di hai aur woh apni ( kitaab ) nasiyaat se munh phair rahay hain
23,72,"kiya tum un se ( tableegh ke siilay mein ) kuch maal mangte ho, to tumhara perwar-digaar ka maal bohat acha hai aur woh sab se behtar rizaq dainay wala hai"
23,73,aur tum to un ko seedhay rastay ki taraf bulatay ho
23,74,aur jo log akhirat par imaan nahi laatay woh raste se allag ho rahay hain
